# Onboarding for Partners

## Access and Permissions
- You have been added as an **Outside Collaborator** to specific repositories.
- You will only see the repositories explicitly shared with you and this central hub.
- Access to this hub is provided to ensure you can follow New Game Plus engineering standards.

## Getting Started
1. Review the [Engineering Standards](../standards/ENGINEERING.md).
2. Ensure **Two-Factor Authentication (2FA)** is enabled on your GitHub account.
3. Clone the project repository assigned to your team.
4. Run the local setup script (usually `setup.sh` or `npm install`) as defined in the project README.

## Support
- For access issues: Contact your internal Project Manager.
- For technical blockers: Use the GitHub Discussions tab in the project repository.
